definitions.definition: A village and civil parish (served by Bainton and Ashton Parish Council) in the City of Peterborough district, Cambridgeshire , England ( OS grid ref TF0906 ) .
A village and civil parish in the East Riding of Yorkshire , England ( OS grid ref SE9652 ) .
A hamlet in Stoke Lyne parish, Cherwell district, Oxfordshire , England ( OS grid ref SP5827 ) .
A habitational surname from Old English .
